Additional Notes
- - - - - - - - -

If you have translated Tefinch to a new language, send us the translation!



Prerequirements for Installation
- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -

 * A running MySQL database (4.1 or greater).
 * A webserver with PHP4 support.



Installation Instructions
- - - - - - - - - - - - - -

- Copy the contents of the "src/" directory to your webserver.

- Edit the file "config.inc.php" according to your needs. It should be self explaining.

- Create your database tables using the file mysql_nested.sql. If you have a rented webspace,
  you usually do this by loading the file in the phpMyAdmin tool provided by your webspace
  provider.

- Done. You can now open the webpage.
